      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Berthold Burg addressed to Hugo Glaser. Burg describes the fate and death of
          his fellow prisoner Max, who was shot in the Fürstengrube labour camp by the camp
          commander. The letter became part of the Documentation campaign, Prague.</p>
      </abstract>




